{"tid":2304353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邵家臻12月1號後冇得再用議員身分幫在囚手足，需要大家課金支持","createTime":"2020-11-28T16:53:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T12:56:50.000Z","uid":302236,"like":63,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"0100062730411815874838463ad20aa13159ca01","tid":2304353,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1AP8r33HRg8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1AP8r33HRg8&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=5e419ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1AP8r33HRg8</a><br />\n<br />\n有寫開信嘅都知邵家臻幫咗在囚手足好多，12月1號之後佢只可以透過一般探訪探手足，冇議員身分唔可以幫被針對在囚手足做啲咩實際野，亦都唔會再有立法會議員批錢去搞一切同在囚手足有關嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n佢喺片入面都有講到話經濟上有困難，佢patreon收入連辦公室一個月開支嘅<span class=\"red\">十分一</span>都冇<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以課金支援下邵家臻，咁佢先可以有足夠經濟能力維持各種同在囚手足聯繫嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/bottleshiukachun\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fbottleshiukachun&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=d258f8fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/bottleshiukachun</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">最後希望大家繼續寫信，繼續去旁聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ba90d205e094fa524af7a80f52fc46dc05ab6411","tid":2304353,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T16:54:17.000Z","msg":"召喚課金師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ca3b0a564a272ccda10428c9ed4fc42f088693","tid":2304353,"uid":3