8r33HRg8</a><br />\n<br />\n有寫開信嘅都知邵家臻幫咗在囚手足好多，12月1號之後佢只可以透過一般探訪探手足，冇議員身分唔可以幫被針對在囚手足做啲咩實際野，亦都唔會再有立法會議員批錢去搞一切同在囚手足有關嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n佢喺片入面都有講到話經濟上有困難，佢patreon收入連辦公室一個月開支嘅<span class=\"red\">十分一</span>都冇<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以課金支援下邵家臻，咁佢先可以有足夠經濟能力維持各種同在囚手足聯繫嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/bottleshiukachun\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fbottleshiukachun&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=d258f8fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/bottleshiukachun</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">最後希望大家繼續寫信，繼續去旁聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1bc1f52aca446e991da123c0e0ae0788a4ed4605","tid":2304353,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"支持佢 入面手足需要更多人關注"},{"pid":"9eb0a25dce38fe5b7891127882e3383ac68807d6","tid":2304353,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T05:37:59.000Z","msg":"其實佢係咪最應留住議席個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有呢個身份可以更有效關注在囚手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過算啦回歸現實再繼續幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fb5544d67c44fc893836fabb7c862153bdb31f","tid":2304353,"uid":560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e41b76b0a5b7a7f22739da8b61526f8cd0eec09","tid":2304353,"uid":302236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eb0a25dce38fe5b7891127882e3383ac68807d6","tid":2304353,"uid":43062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-